<div id="review_3202402799" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3202402799" />
    <a title="Machteld" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/49150181-machteld"><img alt="Machteld" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1608380771p2/49150181.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3202402799?book_show_action=true">Feb 22, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Machteld" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Machteld" href="/user/show/49150181-machteld">Machteld</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3202402799" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6182861154573755288">I loved this book. I like Barbara Woods books in general, but this was one of the best. I really liked the fact that she could take me into a different world so easily. It was very visual. Interesting storylines and it makes you think. I could really relate to the characters and the story felt very real. Not overly romantic, just hardship and struggles, like in real life. Recommended!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

