<span id="freeTextContainer5764703786099959355">An Egyptian soap opera and sometimes it&apos;s fun to read such. Jasmine is banished from her Egyptian family after she becomes pregnant by the evil Hasin who rapes her as she is trying to get his help to save her family from the rebels. Soap opera - oh yes. It&apos;s redeeming quality is the history of Egypt from 1946 to the present. Women had it baaaad in Egypt.</span>
